imdb.title: Kokey
plot: An alien named _Kokey_ (qv) from the planet Yekok had crash-landed on Earth in his ship. He befriends Bong and Anna, two children who help _Kokey_ (qv). Meanwhile, _Kokey_ (qv)'s enemy, Korokoy, followed him to Earth in order to find a crystal _Kokey_ (qv) has.
